headline: Hudson Pacific Properties to Participate in Citi’s 2026 Global Property CEO Conference
summary: LOS ANGELES, February 27, 2026--Hudson Pacific Properties, Inc. (NYSE: HPP) today announced that Victor Coleman, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, and other members of the company’s senior management will participate in a roundtable discussion at Citi’s 2026 Global Property CEO Conference on Monday, March 2, 2026 at 2:10 p.m. ET.

headline: How The J Sainsbury (LSE:SBRY) Story Is Shifting With Tightened Analyst Price Targets
summary: The latest analyst updates on J Sainsbury centre on only small trims to price targets, such as shifts from £3.66 to £3.60 and from £3.50 to £3.45, while one fair value estimate stays anchored at £3.47. Bullish and more cautious analysts are reading the same set of numbers differently, which is why you see both constructive ratings and slightly reduced targets sitting together in the mid £3 range. As you read on, you will see how these moves fit into the wider narrative and how to keep track...
